sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant LAPI as Log API Envelope Provider Plugin Adapter
    participant RM as RoundManager
    participant WL as TIngressWaitingList
    participant RP as ReferencePrecalculator
    participant ING as Ingress
    participant REG as TContainerRegistry
    participant C as TContainer
    participant S as TSlot

    RM->>REG: inspect container state/readiness views
    RM->>WL: register eligible container registry index
    WL->>RP: provide ordered ingress candidate indices
    RP->>REG: resolve container data and slot state
    RP-->>ING: prepare / issue TIngressAccessRef
    LAPI-->>ING: provide prepared envelope
    ING->>S: place envelope through valid ingress ref
    S-->>C: update occupancy/state relation
    C-->>RM: update readiness for next progression
